          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He who keeps the law is a discerning son, But he who is a companion of gluttons humiliates his father. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He who keeps the law is a discerning son, But he who is a companion of gluttons humiliates his father."
